steps.name: I create a random file that is 500KB large, named streammanager-input.log
I create an S3 bucket for testing
I copy the file streammanager-input.log to my device at ${test.context:installRoot}/streammanager-input.log
I create a Greengrass deployment with components
I update my Greengrass deployment configuration, setting the component com.aws.StreamManagerExport configuration to:
I deploy the Greengrass deployment configuration
the Greengrass deployment is COMPLETED on the device after 2 minutes
the aws.greengrass.StreamManager log on the device contains the line "Stream Manager reporting the state: RUNNING" within 30 seconds
the S3 bucket contains the key export/streammanager-input.log within 30 seconds
